<template>
    
<fluent-divider></fluent-divider>
    
</template>

<script>
    import {
    provideFluentDesignSystem,
    fluentDivider
} from "@fluentui/web-components";

provideFluentDesignSystem()
    .register(
        fluentDivider()
    );
export default {
    name: 'OtherWeb'
};

</script>

<style>
  fluent-divider {
  font-family: sans-serif;
  padding: 4px;
}
</style>
